{"tid":962662,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［TG］圍爐取暖問號谷","createTime":"2018-12-31T04:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T11:42:59.000Z","uid":27414,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4b07978b4113e807401c42c358e39ee9003bfd","tid":962662,"uid":27414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T04:51:40.000Z","msg":"本谷年齡層為90後 巴絲都歡迎 <br />\n<br />\n歡迎叫春 分享下生活 分享下興趣<br />\n大家返工返學悶悶地咪入嚟吹下水9UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不定期有聚會 大家俾啲熱誠就成事㗎啦<br />\n活動不外乎食飯飲野partyroom行山運動bbq<br />\n應有盡有 有人提議到就得<br />\n<br />\nPm 記得講埋基本自我介紹<br />\n名 幾歲 有咩興趣 等等<br />\n或者你有咩想同我地分享都可以講埋<br />\n<br />\n希望呢一個谷可以成為你哋開心同唔開心嘅樹窿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLINK：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wtsns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwtsns&d=fCOYiJelhX8M7wCogUqPFjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=74aaa34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wtsns</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wtsns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwtsns&d=fCOYiJelhX8M7wCogUqPFjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=74aaa34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wtsns</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wtsns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwtsns&d=fCOYiJelhX8M7wCogUqPFjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=74aaa34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wtsns</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wtsns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwtsns&d=fCOYiJelhX8M7wCogUqPFjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=74aaa34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wtsns</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wtsns\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwtsns&d=fCOYiJelhX8M7wCogUqPFjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=74aaa34c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wtsns</a><br />\n<br />\n#